<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MYPD 마이데이터의 첫걸음</title>

    
    <!-- SWIPER -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css"/>
    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/default.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/logo-fabicon.png">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about_nav">
        <nav class="navigation">
            <div class="top">
                <h1><a href="/main"><img src = "../images/logo.png" width="230px" height="100%" alt="MYPD" class="logo"></a></h1>
                <div class="menu">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/main#scroll_about">About</a></li>
                        <li><a href="">Mypage</a></li>
                        <li style="margin-right: 40px;"><a href="/main#scroll_contact">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <a class="login_box" href="/user/login" >로그인</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <main>
        <div class="main_pic_bg">
            <div class="city_edit"> 
                <h1>회원정보 수정</h1>
                <p>여러분의 서비스와 테스트데이터를 등록하세요.</p>
  
                <div class="mypage_menu">
                  <div class="mypage_menuBtn"> 마이데이터 서비스 테스트 관리 </div>
                  <!-- editdata / editmty 나눠야함 -->
                  <a href="../mypage/editdata" class="mypage_menuBtn" >테스트 데이터 관리</a>
                  <div class="mypage_menuBtn"> 연동 테스트 </div>
                  <div class="mypage_menuBtn"> 테스트 현황 </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 비밀번호 재확인 -->
                <div class="mypage_box">
                    <div class="img">
                        <img src="../images/sad.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="edit_pw_check_txt">등록된 테스트 데이터가 없어요</h1>
                    <p>테스트 데이터를 등록하고 테스트데이터를 관리하세요</p>
                    <p>테스트데이터가 없다면 샘플데이터를  사용할 수 있어요</p>

                    <div class="editData_btn" style="margin-top: 20px;"><button style="background-color: #888888;">테스트 데이터 추가하기</button></div>
                    <div class="editData_btn"><button>샘플 데이터 다운받기</button></div>

                </div>

          </div>
    <div class="input">
      <form class="loginBox" method="POST" action="/user/login">
        <div class="inputBox">
          <img src="../images/id.png" alt="" id="loginImg">
          <input type="text" id="id" name="id" placeholder="Enter your username" >
        </div>
        <div class="inputBox">
          <img src="../images/pw.png" alt="" id="loginImg" width="30px">
          <input type="password" id="id" name="pw" placeholder="Enter your password" >
        </div>
        <div class="btn">
          <button type="submit" class="loginBtn"><strong>로그인</strong></button><br>
        </div>
      </form>
      <div class="btn" style="display: flex;">
        <a href="/user/find_main" class="findidpw">아이디/비밀번호 찾기</a>
        <p style="color: #7B7B7B;">아직 회원이 아니신가요?</p>
        <button type="button" class="makeId"><strong>회원가입</strong></button>
        <!-- a태그 추가해 redirect 해주기 -->
      </div>
      <div class="btn" id="snsLogin">
        <p style="color: #7B7B7B;">다른 계정으로 로그인하기</p>
        <div class="icon">
          <button type="button" class="snsBtn"><img src="../images/naver.png" alt="" id="snsImg"></button>
          <button type="button" class="snsBtn"><img src="../images/kakao.png" alt="" id="snsImg"></button>
          <button type="button" class="snsBtn"><img src="../images/facebook.png" alt="" id="snsImg"></button>
          <button type="button" class="snsBtn"><img src="../images/google.png" alt="" id="snsImg"></button>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>